Details:
MEGASOFT is an educational institution and a great place to study with highly qualified, certified and experienced faculty members who offer an excellent learning environment.MEGASOFT provides QUALITY TRAINING to all the students who want to make their Dream Career in IT, Management or any professional field. We also provide various IT and IT enabled solutions & services and try to motivate and promote the students of Bihar in becoming the world class skilled professionals in these sectors.MEGASOFT is one of the best premiere educational institutions in Patna. Details: Frameboxx Animation & Visual Effects is a versatile conglomerate with a focus on providing high end media and entertainment training & related services. Started in 2007 by a team of management and technical evangelists with over ten years of experience in the Animation & Visual effects production & training domain, Frameboxx offers a wide array of training programs aimed at producing high quality trained manpower to fuel lndia's Media & Entertainment industry. Ever since our inception, we've expanded our presence to over fifty state of the art training studios spread across India. Frameboxx is a division of Ideacount Education Pvt. Ltd., a multi-faceted organization with a focus on empowering high quality education brands in the country.At Frameboxx, our core competence and industry experience has allowed us to expand our service domain to offer a wide array of services across multiple verticals such as career specialization courses in Animation, Visual Effects and Film Making including Degree Courses, Pastel IP for Web, Print & Broadcast, Clickboxx.tv for Online Training, Designboxx for Design & Art School Preparatory courses and ProCAMPUS for top tier short courses with top industry experts. We're happy to have a positive mandate from the industry as well as our students who've equally done us proud by winning awards and accolades at some of the most prestigious festivals and competitions worldwide.Frameboxx believes in working closely with the industry and the same is reflected in our tie-ups with some of the most prestigious institutions and experts from across the world. We have a strategic tie-up with Sikkim Manipal University's Directorate of Distance Education for offering their Bachelors of Science in Multimedia & Animation course and with visual effects veteran Mr. Steve Wright for our Nuke Digital Compositing program. We believe good companies are built by people and we have seen this statement re-enforced by a strong team of some of the finest instructors in the country who have been the foundation strength of Frameboxx Animation & Visual Effects right from day one.In a market that is saturated by animation training providers, Frameboxx brings fresh energy and innovation and a commitment to quality that is unparalleled. Our objective to venture into training and education stems from our years of industry experience coupled with extensive research and analysis of various trends which were affecting animation training quality in the country. Our research dictated the need to single out skills during training to create techno-artistes and specialists. This led to the development of India's first ever skill set specialization based program which enables a student to pursue his domain of interest and develop a strong skill around it. This also meant that students not only perform better but strive to perfect their skill and become specialists. Our specialization training curriculum has been carefully designed with a global perspective in mind and offers the latest in technology and technique.Frameboxx is not just any other Media & Entertainment training brand. We invite you to visit your nearest Frameboxx training studio and be a part of this exciting and animated industry.
